{"tid":1253991,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"Netflix英配版《新世紀福音戰士》修改渚薰台詞「Love」變「Like」引發觀眾不滿","createTime":"2019-06-24T01:18:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T08:14:49.000Z","uid":75050,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c131ff16a88832a49599f6ee7467596b9f6856ac","tid":1253991,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T01:18:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hkacger.com/archives/88122/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Farchives%2F88122%2F&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr1%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=ba4dc296\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkacger.com/archives/88122/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/00-51.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2F00-51.jpg%3F&h=2c911f32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>不說&rdquo;愛&rdquo;而是說&rdquo;喜歡&rdquo;，觀眾不滿《新世紀福音戰士》Netflix英配版修改渚薰台詞</ins></strong><br />\n作者: 填海紳士 日期: 23/06/2019<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/EVA.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2FEVA.jpg%3F&h=66f81b57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說Netflix最近全球上架了神作《新世紀福音戰士》的TV動畫和兩部舊劇場版<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eAGvFelW7rM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeAGvFelW7rM&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr1%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=88ca853b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eAGvFelW7rM</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LnC2bmS9cBI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLnC2bmS9cBI&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr1%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=4dc687a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LnC2bmS9cBI</a><br />\n<br />\n英配版令觀眾們不滿的理由相當多，當中讓很多人難以接受的是Netflix改動了渚薰的台詞<br />\n<br />\n包括由&rdquo;It means, I love you&rdquo;改成意思更模糊的&rdquo;It means I like you&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/01-27.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2F01-27.jpg%3F&h=26f231ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n很多網友就認為這是Netflix故意&rdquo;和諧&rdquo;碇真嗣與渚薰的關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D9lWSW5VAAACXCB.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FD9lWSW5VAAACXCB.jpg%3F&h=78cc875e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外還有把某幕經典場景中碇真嗣的台詞由 &ldquo;I&rsquo;m so f***ed up.&rdquo;改做 &ldquo;lowest of the low.&rdquo;<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D9kdiU_UEAIf--C.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FD9kdiU_UEAIf--C.jpg%3F&h=66737279&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b123c3137f33eba66ae4c441e92cf986d1f631b5","tid":1253991,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T01:19:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c2e8c810ee0eb0d82ca8ca19c1d9e06b314d7f9","tid":1253991,"uid":40101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T01:26:23.000Z","msg":"電視版ED無左都吊晒鬼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3001f2551ead9f7d6b6e683e6516f7cdc8ac8ef","tid":1253991,"uid":75050,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T04:16:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"874825f5d67ddcb164ae59c311e9f916e4fc2d88","tid":1253991,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T10:23:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5962fff87da9d0a5fe22a4f7ee11436b6b6e6599","tid":1253991,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"